DRAW
layout-engine: elk
theme-id: 4
title: |md
  # Lock-free Hash Map Architecture
| {near: top-center}
LFHashMap {
  buckets: _Atomic(BucketEntry*)
  bucket_count: _Atomic(uint64_t)
  element_count: _Atomic(uint64_t)
  resize_version: _Atomic(uint64_t)
  head: HashMapNode*
}
BucketEntry {
  sentinel: _Atomic(HashMapNode*)
}
HashMapNode {
  so_key: uint64_t
  key: void*
  value: void*
  next: HashMapNode* (marked)
}
LFHashMap.buckets -> BucketEntry
BucketEntry.sentinel -> HashMapNode: "Points into\nsplit-ordered list"
LFHashMap.head -> HashMapNode: "List head\n(dummy)"
HashMapNode.next -> HashMapNode: "Sorted by so_key"
note: |md
  - Buckets are **indexes** into the split-ordered list
  - **No rehashing** on resize
  - Buckets initialized **lazily**
| {near: bottom-center}